{"tid":1274852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請將今晚定義為「香港太陽花運動」","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T01:37:16.000Z","uid":89160,"like":81,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4709b7f49e5fed98763d84e707a2e5bae8d95d","tid":1274852,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>原因1：將香港發生既事，盡量同世界各地抗爭扯上關係，爭取國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n原因2：台灣法庭判定 22 名太陽花抗爭者無罪。咁樣去比較，會更加容易明白抗爭既正當性。就算一旦有人被秋後算帳，都可以係開庭前帶動輿論。</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實今日比台灣太陽花既形勢更險峻，台灣係民選政權始終要避忌三分，但林鄭根本唔需要睇香港人面色，今日係靠義士捨身堅持，先可以令七一不致無聲無色，希望大家真係明白不割席既重要性。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"a6bc52b55066e81a5681d24aba2971933cc96f24","tid":1274852,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0737e04790772394419bb8b16c8fec857912aa2d","tid":1274852,"uid":194573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">下次行動要點做先對得住義士?</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274782</a>"},{"pid":"1ae58a07e616bb8a4109172350abccbc792b8155","tid":1274852,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c543c17629825179ed05e53afc1c6cf7915cd5c6","tid":1274852,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:30:01.000Z","msg":"歡迎指教"},{"pid":"00b049e50db13be34b41b8267fd62a5a83867583","tid":1274852,"uid":104138,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:31:02.000Z","msg":"應該係黑色洋紫荊運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0290fa4fd5b04a659384830a1c5f38202524bf81","tid":1274852,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b049e50db13be34b41b8267fd62a5a83867